collections.name: TICA - A Roots Brazilian Caramel
collections.description: This is Tica. She was born and raised in the countryside. She is a mixed breed dog, or commonly called a "stray dog". She is a swimmer, runner, hunter (she was often hunted), playful, loving, and protective. She likes to give everyone her paw, with a very serene look. She has a keen sixth sense. She supports us in the most difficult moments. She is very loved. She has several scars on her body, from confrontations with agoutis, armadillos, wild boars, being run over, etc. She lived among rivers, streams, fields, dirt roads, in the middle of sugar cane, dust, rain, storms, scorching heat, even though she always had a little corner to stay and rest. She loves nature! This NFT is to celebrate the life of Tica, who is now adapting to the city, keeping me and my mother company, after the death of my beloved father. This NFT is a tribute for us to share with the world through you, about the life and infinite love we receive for free from this divine creature.

collections.name: F.U.C.K A.R.T
collections.description:
F.U.C.K A.R.T – NFT Collection of Everyday Moments

Welcome to F.U.C.K A.R.T, an NFT collection that captures the beauty, irony, and raw truth of everyday moments. This is where the ordinary becomes extraordinary, reimagined with a touch of humor, a dash of provocation, and a whole lot of artistic flair.

This collection is more than just art—it's a celebration of life's overlooked details: the too-strong coffee, the unexpected joy in chaos, or the absurdity of reality turning into art.

F.U.C.K A.R.T is authentic, unfiltered, and unapologetic. It's art that doesn’t conform to glossy perfection but instead reveals the genuine, unpolished facets of daily life. Each NFT tells its own story—sometimes ironic, sometimes profound, always real.

Dive in, discover the magic in the mundane, and join a movement that proves art is everywhere, if you know where to look.

collections.name: MetaSelfys
collections.description:
Welcome to MetaSelfys, a unique NFT art collection that brings a nostalgic twist to the digital art world. Inspired by the beloved yet now-obsolete MMO game TinierMe, which closed its doors in 2012, MetaSelfys breathes new life into the cherished characters from this virtual universe.

About:
MetaSelfys is a collection of meticulously crafted NFTs, each representing a unique original character from the TinierMe universe. These characters, once part of a vibrant online community, have been reimagined and immortalized on the blockchain, ensuring their legacy endures in the digital realm.

Unique Original Characters: 
Every NFT in the MetaSelfys collection is a one-of-a-kind piece.

No Copyright Infringement: MetaSelfys is created with respect for the original game and its creators. All characters are original and unique, ensuring no copyright infringement.

WIP: website and other social media pages.
